BT /F2 20 Tf 1 0 0 1 52 782 Tm (Special Report: How SQL Server Was Used in) Tj ET
BT /F2 20 Tf 1 0 0 1 52 756 Tm (This Project) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 1 0 0 1 52 716 Tm (1. Purpose of SQL Server in the Project) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 52 691 Tm (SQL Server is the core data layer of the Kenya Environment Portal. It stores all) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 52 676 Tm (structured information used by both the public website and the administrator dashboard.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 52 661 Tm (SSMS 22 is used to create the database, inspect tables, run queries, and test that the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 52 646 Tm (system is working correctly.) Tj ET
