BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 58 297 Tm (   programs, incidents, and admin users.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 58 282 Tm (6. Creates the function and stored procedure used for records indexing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 58 267 Tm (7. Rebuilds the knowledge index at the end of the script.) Tj ET
