BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 58 519 Tm (4. If the login is successful, the session is created in Flask.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 58 504 Tm (5. SQL updates LastLoginAt.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 58 489 Tm (6. SQL inserts an audit entry in dbo.AdminActivityLog.) Tj ET
